  "body": "After migration to React 15.1.0 I noticed that my application is running slower than usual. Quick debug with Chrome profiler shows that  method `purgeUnmountedComponents` from `ReactComponentTreeDevtool` eats around 30% of my application time. On every mouse move or click method iterates over huge amount of elements. I don't know if that behaviour is desirable.\n\n![reactperfcpu](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2017454/15851913/54cbed52-2c9f-11e6-90bd-915aeb4e58a1.PNG)\n",
